videos.description: Duke's press works perfectly as Jack White steals the inbounds pass, then bounces the ball to Wendell Moore Jr. for the layup and the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (White steals inbounds pass and feeds Moore for bucket plus foul) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: White steals inbounds pass and feeds Moore for bucket plus foul

videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. blocks the shot on defense, then is rewarded with a strong layup down low off the assist from Jordan Goldwire.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Carey swats shot, then muscles in for layup) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Carey swats shot, then muscles in for layup

videos.description: Tre Jones lobs the ball in on the inbounds play to Cassius Stanley who hammers it down with one hand.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanley throws down monster jam on inbounds play) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Stanley throws down monster jam on inbounds play

videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. swats John Comeaux's shot with his right hand and then again with his left hand.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Carey blocks the same shot twice) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Carey blocks the same shot twice

videos.description: Kevon Harris makes the good lead pass to Cameron Johnson for the game-tying layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Harris leads Johnson for the big Stephen F. Austin layup) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Harris leads Johnson for the big Stephen F. Austin layup

videos.description: Vernon Carey Jr. gets the block, which leads to Cassius Stanley's big triple on the other end.
videos.headline: Carey's block leads to Stanley's 3

videos.description: Stephen F. Austin nearly loses in crushing fashion as the ball goes right to Cassius Stanley, but he can't get the game-winning shot attempt to go.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stanley can't hit game winner as game goes to OT) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Stanley can't hit game winner as game goes to OT

videos.description: Stephen F. Austin's Nathan Bain comes away with the loose ball and dribbles the length of the court to score the game-winning layup as time expires.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Stephen F. Austin wins on breakaway layup in OT) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Stephen F. Austin stuns No. 1 Duke with OT buzzer-beater

videos.description: Duke coach Mike Krzyzewski gives credit to Stephen F. Austin for their upset win over the Blue Devils, saying they won the game with their toughness.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_Presser (Coach K on Stephen F. Austin: 'They were better') 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Coach K on Stephen F. Austin: 'They were better'

videos.description: Stephen F. Austin's players give head coach Kyle Keller a Gatorade shower in the locker room after their monumental upset against No. 1 Duke.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Misc. (Stephen F. Austin players douse coach with Gatorade) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Stephen F. Austin players douse coach with Gatorade
